207061.name: Glorious School Life
207061.desc: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?

207032.name: Illustrious Ball
207032.desc: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

207110.name: Illustrious μ
207110.desc: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

301056.name: Covert Ops Cloak
301056.desc: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...

207023.name: New Year's Protectress
207023.desc: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.

207031.name: Never-Ending Tea Party
207031.desc: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

206061.name: Unfamiliar Duties
206061.desc: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

301057.name: Low-Key Idol @Confused
301057.desc: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?

207010.name: Eagle
207010.desc: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)

301050.name: Ayanami
301050.desc: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.

301120.name: Inazuma
301120.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number four - Inazuma.

301020.name: Shirayuki
301020.desc: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.

207042.name: Guidance of the Spring Goddess
207042.desc: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!

301021.name: Bunny Breeder
301021.desc: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!

213040.name: Abercrombie
213040.desc: Roberts-class monitor - Abercrombie. Hull Number F109.

207033.name: Resplendent Hibiscus
207033.desc: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

301053.name: Rock 'n' Demon
301053.desc: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?

207041.name: The Goddess' Day Off
207041.desc: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!

213021.name: Halloween Terror
213021.desc: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?

207020.name: Ark Royal
207020.desc: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!

207090.name: Little Illustrious
207090.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.

207028.name: Pure-White Protector
207028.desc: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!

207011.name: Eagle's Clinic
207011.desc: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.

301110.name: Ikazuchi
301110.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number three - Ikazuchi.

207052.name: Timeless Classics
207052.desc: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

207060.name: Glorious
207060.desc: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.

213011.name: Illusory Happiness
213011.desc: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

207035.name: Maiden Lily's Radiance
207035.desc: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

301011.name: 5 Minutes Till I'm Late
301011.desc: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!

207051.name: The Lady of the Beach
207051.desc: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.

207022.name: Guardian of the Ball
207022.desc: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!

206052.name: Gamer Style
206052.desc: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

301131.name: Is The Order A Torpedo?
301131.desc: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

301123.name: Dusk's Lightning
301123.desc: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?

207030.name: Illustrious
207030.desc: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!

206060.name: Perseus
206060.desc: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)

213012.name: Wardrobe Witchery
213012.desc: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

301122.name: Flash of Fireworks
301122.desc: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

207038.name: Morning Star of Love and Hope
207038.desc: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

301059.name: Ayanami (Retrofit)
301059.desc: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...

213020.name: Terror
213020.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!

301121.name: Vanilla Pudding
301121.desc: It doesn’t matter if {namecode:14} becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if {namecode:14} cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey {namecode:14}'s heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——

301113.name: Dawn's Thunder
301113.desc: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?

301112.name: Thunderous Festival
301112.desc: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?

301013.name: Music Pixy
301013.desc: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

301111.name: Sakura Tea
301111.desc: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!

207021.name: Coast Watcher
207021.desc: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!

206051.name: The Way of the Dragon Empery
206051.desc: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

301101.name: New Year's Little Imp
301101.desc: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!

301100.name: Hibiki
301100.desc: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.

207029.name: Ark Royal (Retrofit)
207029.desc: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!

301055.name: Grade A Sailor Uniform
301055.desc: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

301091.name: Akatsuki Goes North
301091.desc: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!

301058.name: Demon's Finest Dress
301058.desc: This dress is... {namecode:6}’s. I'm not used to this dress yet... Commander, do you think it fits me?

301092.name: Motoninja Akatsuki
301092.desc: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!

213041.name: Pumpkin Blast!
213041.desc: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

301051.name: Witch in Ambush
301051.desc: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

301015.name: Stormy Waitress-in-Training!
301015.desc: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...

301014.name: Fubuki Halation!
301014.desc: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!

301012.name: Mascot Bucky
301012.desc: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...

213042.name: Mischief on the Rocks
213042.desc: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

301054.name: Lunar Demon
301054.desc: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

213010.name: Erebus
213010.desc: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!

207062.name: Pungent Plum
207062.desc: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!
